sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Campaign Moderator
    participant UI as UI
    participant BFF as Campaign BFF
    participant CS as Campaign Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>UI: Open Campaign Prioritization screen
    UI->>BFF: GET /campaigns/{campaignId}/prioritization-config
    BFF->>CS: GET /campaigns/{campaignId}/prioritization-config
    CS->>DB: Read stages and questions
    DB-->>CS: Existing config
    CS-->>BFF: Prioritization config
    BFF-->>UI: Prioritization config for screen load

    User->>UI: Click Add Stage
    User->>UI: Enter stage name and weightage
    Note over UI: Stage added in local screen state only

    User->>UI: Select stage
    User->>UI: Click Add Question
    User->>UI: Enter question, scale, weightage
    Note over UI: Question added in local screen state only

    User->>UI: Click Save / Submit
    UI->>UI: Validate stage total weight = 100
    UI->>UI: Validate question weights per stage
    UI->>BFF: PUT /campaigns/{campaignId}/prioritization-config

    BFF->>CS: Forward consolidated payload
    CS->>CS: Validate business rules
    CS->>DB: Begin transaction
    CS->>DB: Upsert prioritization stages
    CS->>DB: Upsert prioritization questions
    CS->>DB: Delete removed stages/questions
    CS->>DB: Commit transaction

    DB-->>CS: Save successful
    CS-->>BFF: Success response
    BFF-->>UI: Configuration saved successfully
    UI-->>User: Show success message